  "original_title": "\u0b90\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b85\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0baf\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0baa\u0baf !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "To travel to the United Arab Kingdom or Singapore, there is a million dollars waiting in the Maldives!",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to airport information, Sri Lankan President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and his partner Ayoma Rajapaksa, who have visited Maldives, have been accommodated in a special guest room at Velana Airport in Maldives.",
        "Velana airport information says that they are preparing to travel specifically to the United Arab Kingdom or Singapore.",
        "At the same time, it is reported that the Maldivian side has shown no desire to allow President Gotabaya Rajapaksa into their country and make the necessary arrangements."
      ],
